---
// TheLeak.astro
// Block 2: The Leak
// Grid Layout: 2-Column Split | 50/50 Weight (Mobile: Single Stack)
// Container Physics: [Height: 100vh] | [Scroll: Snap-Point]
---

<section id="the-leak" class="min-h-screen w-full flex items-start md:items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-8 snap-start relative border-t border-surface/30 section-pt">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-24 items-center">
    
    <!-- Left Column: Copy (The Cost) -->
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <!-- Problem Keyword (H2 | VR3) -->
      <h2 class="text-xs md:text-sm font-body font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent mb-4">
        Poor digital architecture's costs
      </h2>
      
      <!-- Problem Hook (H3 | VR2) -->
      <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight text-text-heading mb-6">
        The Invisible Leaks of a "Sandy" Foundation
      </h3>
      
      <!-- Context Copy (P | Body) -->
      <p class="text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Prioritizing costs and practicality when laying your digital foundations isn't smart. That choice often results in fragile code, poor infrastructure, and unplanned costs that harm your business.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Your fragile digital foundation isn't something you can "tweak"&mdash;it's a persistent<strong class="text-text-heading">capital-draining liability</strong>.
      </p>
      
      <!-- The Verdict (H4 | VR3) -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-surface/50 border-l-4 border-error mb-8">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-text-heading">
          Stop spending on foundations that cannot scale.
        </h4>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Right Column: Risk Visual (Conceptual Diagram) -->
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-full aspect-square relative opacity-90" role="img" aria-label="Conceptual diagram: A website under maintenance equals no revenue (euro symbol crossed out).">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 500 300" class="w-full h-full text-text-heading" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Website Frame (Squared) -->
        <g transform="translate(50, 50)">
          <rect x="0" y="0" width="160" height="160" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4" />
          <rect x="0" y="0" width="160" height="25" fill="currentColor" />
          <!-- Browser UI dots -->
          <circle cx="15" cy="12.5" r="3" fill="var(--color-primary-base, #000)" opacity="0.5" />
          <circle cx="30" cy="12.5" r="3" fill="var(--color-primary-base, #000)" opacity="0.5" />
          <circle cx="45" cy="12.5" r="3" fill="var(--color-primary-base, #000)" opacity="0.5" />
          
          <!-- Maintenance Icon (Wrench & Screwdriver) -->
          <!-- Centered in the 160x160 box. Original center approx (125, 100) in 256x241 -->
          <g transform="translate(-15, 15) scale(0.75)">
            <path d="M169.385,132.8c0.131,1.179,0,2.575-0.306,3.885l-11.131-10.258l-10.04,10.957l11.262,10.214c-1.31,0.437-2.575,0.742-3.885,0.742c-3.885,0.131-7.203-1.048-10.04-3.623c-2.837-2.706-4.365-5.849-4.496-9.734c0-1.353,0.131-2.881,0.437-4.191l-2.706-2.575l-16.195-14.798l-27.413,30.207c-1.659,2.226-4.234,3.754-7.203,3.754c-4.802,0-8.687-3.885-8.687-8.687c0-2.575,1.004-4.933,2.968-6.591l28.461-29.509L93.213,86.835c-1.353,0.611-2.881,0.917-4.191,0.917c-3.885,0.131-7.203-1.048-10.04-3.623s-4.365-5.718-4.496-9.603c-0.131-1.179,0-2.575,0.306-3.885l11.262,10.214l9.953-10.913L84.745,59.728c1.179-0.437,2.575-0.742,3.885-0.742c3.885-0.131,7.203,1.048,10.04,3.623c2.837,2.532,4.365,5.849,4.496,9.734c0.131,1.31,0,2.575-0.306,3.885l17.723,16.238l12.965-14.012l-19.381-17.068l17.592-20.036l49.807,43.826l-17.592,20.036l-19.905-17.548l-12.528,14.798l19.469,17.81c1.31-0.437,2.575-0.742,3.885-0.742c3.885-0.131,7.203,1.048,10.04,3.623C167.77,125.685,169.298,128.828,169.385,132.8z" fill="currentColor" />
          </g>
        </g>

        <!-- Equal Sign -->
        <g transform="translate(240, 130)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round">
          <line x1="0" y1="-12" x2="50" y2="-12" />
          <line x1="0" y1="12" x2="50" y2="12" />
        </g>

        <!-- Negative Revenue (Minus + Euro) -->
        <g transform="translate(400, 130)">
          <!-- Red Minus Symbol -->
          <line x1="-80" y1="0" x2="-45" y2="0" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="10" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <!-- Euro Symbol -->
          <path d="M30,-40 A40,40 0 1,0 30,40 M-15,-10 h35 M-15,10 h35" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" />
        </g>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>
